    What's special

    An outstanding investment opportunity or owner-occupant property awaits in the heart of Olde Towne East! This remarkable 2.5-story brick duplex on a DOUBLE Lot showcases meticulous craftsmanship and thoughtful updates. The renovated side (831), previously owner-occupied, pairs seamlessly with the well-maintained adjoining residence (829). Situated on a rare double lot, this property offers a private urban retreat with a fenced yard, patio, and a 2-car garage. You'll find timeless architectural character, including coffered ceilings, rich wood floors, crown molding, and solid wood doors. The updated kitchens and baths are designed for lasting appeal, making this home ideal for both owners and tenants. Currently 100% rented. Curb offers only. Will Show with an accepted purchase offer.
